Package net.user1.union.core.event

Interface Summary
Event All events dispatched in the server implement the Event interface.
EventProducer An EventProducer is capable of dispatching events to listeners who have registered to receive those events.
RemoteEvent A RemoteEvent is an event dispatched across a cluster.
RemoteEventProducer A RemoteEventProducer can dispatch events that are re-dispatched by the equivalent objects across the cluster.
 

Class Summary
AccountEvent AccountEvent is a simple data class used to pass information from an account to registered event-listeners when an event occurs.
BaseEvent This is the base class for all events dispatched in the server.
ClientEvent ClientEvent is a simple data class used to pass information from a client to registered event-listeners when a client event occurs.
ModuleEvent ModuleEvent is a simple data class used to pass information from a module to registered event-listeners when a module event occurs.
RemoteRoomEvent RemoteRoomEvent is a simple data class used to pass information from a room to registered event-listeners when a remote room event occurs.
RemoteServerEvent RemoteServerEvent is a simple data class used to pass information from the server to registered event-listeners when a remote server event occurs.
RoomEvent RoomEvent is a simple data class used to pass information from a room to registered event-listeners when a room event occurs.
ServerEvent ServerEvent is a simple data class used to pass information from the server to registered event-listeners when a server event occurs.
UPCEvent UPCEvent is a simple data class used to pass information about a UPCEvent to registered event-listeners.
